team.description: DevFest team has never been more diverse! It has united [GDG Berlin](https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-berlin/), [GDG Berlin Android](https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-berlin-android/), [GDG Berlin Golang](https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-berlin-golang/), [GDG Cloud Berlin](https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-cloud-berlin/), [Women TechMakers](https://gdg.community.dev/women-techmakers-berlin/), [Flutter Berlin](https://www.meetup.com/en-US/flutter-berlin/) and [Kotlin User Group Berlin](https://www.meetup.com/en-US/kotlin-berlin/). They are independant groups of tech enthusiasts who create exciting events and share their passion for various technologies.
